### **4. 30_StreamGraphFlow**  
**Description:**  
Displays real-time numerical input as a flowing line graph with scrollable history.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamGraphFlow - Real-Time Data Visualizer

StreamGraphFlow makes it easy to monitor live data for metrics, dashboards, or system diagnostics.

## Features
- Real-time charting  
- Scrollable view  
- Lightweight + smooth  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/30_StreamGraphFlow.git
cd 30_StreamGraphFlow
python visualize.py
